@section section_root_dir /
This is the root directory of the libxrb package.  It contains configuration
files for Doxygen, Autoconf and Automake, as well as project files for use
in KDevelop, and finally the standard INSTALL, LICENSE and README files found
in almost all packages.

Files
    <ul>
    <li>Doxyfile</li>
    <li>INSTALL</li>
    <li>LICENSE</li>
    <li>Makefile.am</li>
    <li>README</li>
    <li>bootstrap.sh</li>
    <li>configure.ac</li>
    <li>libxrb.kdevelop</li>
    <li>libxrb.kdevelop.filelist</li>
    </ul>

@section section_app /app/
This directory stores a single subdirectory for each of the example/utility
applications that come with XuqRijBuh.  It also contains the top-level
Makefile.am for building all the provided applications.

Files
    <ul>
    <li>Makefile.am</li>
    </ul>

@section section_app_mapeditor2 /app/mapeditor2/
Contains the application harness for the 2-dimensional map editor provided
in @ref section_lib_mapeditor2 "/lib/mapeditor2/" and the Makefile.am
which supplies the rules to compile it.

Files
    <ul>
    <li>Makefile.am</li>
    </ul>

@section section_app_unittest /app/unittest/
The unittest application is housed here.

Files
    <ul>
    <li>Makefile.am</li>
    </ul>

@section section_app_unittest_tests /app/unittest/tests/
This directory contains implementations of the @ref UnitTest interface,
which are each a series of tests for various systems of libxrb.

@section section_doc /doc/
Root directory for storing all documentation source.

@section section_doc_doxygen_pages /doc/doxygen_pages/
Stores all the Doxygen source files for the non-API sections of the
documentation for XuqRijBuh.

@section section_lib /lib/
Top level directory containing all the library code for XuqRijBuh.  This
directory also contains the Makefile.am which gives the rules for building
the library.

Files
    <ul>
    <li>Makefile.am</li>
    </ul>

