@section section_lib_core_serializers /lib/core/serializers/
Contains all the pre-made implementations of the
@ref Xrb::Serializer "Serializer" interface.  You may of course write your
own custom implementations of @c Serializer .

Contents
    <ul>
    <li>@ref Xrb::BinaryFileSerializer </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::CompressionSerializer </li>
    </ul>

@section section_lib_engine2 /lib/engine2/
Back-end functionality for the operation of games.  This directory contains
code that can be thought of as exclusively "server side".  In other words,
no rendering code or user interface elements.

Contents
    <ul>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::Compound </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::Entity </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::Object </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::ObjectLayer </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::PhysicsHandler </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::Polygon </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::QuadTree </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::Sprite </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::SpriteEntity </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::World </li>
    </ul>

@section section_lib_engine2_physicshandlers /lib/engine2/physicshandlers/
Contains all the pre-made implementations of the
@ref Xrb::Engine2::PhysicsHandler "Engine2::PhysicsHandler" interface.
Like @c Serializer , you may write your own custom implementations of
@c PhysicsHandler (this is expected because each game is likely to have its
own unique style of physics handling).

Contents
    <ul>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::PlanetaryPhysicsHandler </li>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::UniformGravityPhysicsHandler </li>
    </ul>

