@section section_lib_render /lib/render/
Contains code relevant to rendering to screen, and the
@ref render_stack "render stack" -- code that can be considered exclusively
"client-side" (no graphical rendering takes place on a server-only
configuration.  Note that there are two classes from the render stack that
reside in the @ref Xrb::Engine2 "Engine2" namespace.  These are here because
they are not "server-side", but rather "client-side".

Contents
    <ul>
    <li>@ref Xrb::Engine2::WorldView </li>
